item.description: Deep Learning Resources Here are two popular and powerful machine learning libraries used for deep learning: TensorFlow Install the latest TensorFlow version in your Python virtual environment by activating the virtual environment and running the following commands in the terminal: conda install tensorflow-gpu -y PyTorch Install the latest PyTorch version in your Python virtual environment by activating the virtual environment and running the following command: conda install pytorch torchvision -y
